Stephen (Steve) Hasker 

		
		Global President and COO, 

	
		 Nielsen Company 	

 
Last Updated: 02/05/2017 



Executive Summary
Hasker has served as the Global President and Chief Operating Officer at Nielsen since January 2016. He previously served as Global President of the Company. Hasker joined Nielsen in 2009 as President for Global Media Products and Advertiser Solutions and was appointed as President for Global Product Leadership in 2013. Prior to joinin 
Personal Attributes and Interests

Hasker is a former Australian track and field athlete
He lectures regularly at Columbia University and NYU. His research into the influence of social networks on consumer behavior in media has been published in the Harvard Busi 
Current Focus

