Key Challenges

Criticism in Survey Method: Nielsen is paying little attention to digital streaming while analyzing television viewership much the way it did in rabbit ears era, according to a 2016 Digital Journal article. Now Nielsen  
Biographical Highlights

Born c. 1969 in Australia.
Hasker holds an undergraduate degree in Economics from the University of Melbourne and went on to earn an MBA and a master’s in International Affairs, both with honors, from Columbia University. 
Other Boards and Organizations

Former Member, Board of Directors, Junior Achievement of New York
Member, Board of Directors, Advertising Research Foundation 
 





